message.content: cs.CR, cs.IOT, cs.SE, cs.OS, cs.SY - The paper discusses the implementation and deployment of secure services for IoT devices, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR) and IoT (cs.IOT). It also mentions the use of a free-software framework (cs.SE) called OP-TEE, which is used to implement trusted applications and services for TrustZone. The paper also evaluates the performance of the framework on common Raspberry Pi hardware platforms, which involves operating systems (cs.OS) and system-level design and implementation (cs.SY).
